 property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">NFL</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/term/nba" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">NBA</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/term/nhl" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">NHL</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/term/mlb" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">MLB</a></div></div></div><div class="social-share bottom"><a href="http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tinyurl.com%2Fy4a2veu6&amp;text=Legalized%20Sports%20Betting%20%E2%80%93%20On%20The%20Horizon%20For%20Michigan%3F" class="social-share-item twitter" title="Tweet" target="_blank">Tweet</a><a href="http://facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tinyurl.com%2Fy4a2veu6&amp;t=Legalized%20Sports%20Betting%20%E2%80%93%20On%20The%20Horizon%20For%20Michigan%3F" class="social-share-item facebook" title="Share" target="_blank">Share</a><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tinyurl.com%2Fy4a2veu6" class="social-share-item googleplus" title="Google+" target="_blank">Google+</a><a href="mailto:?subject=Legalized%20Sports%20Betting%20%E2%80%93%20On%20The%20Horizon%20For%20Michigan%3F&amp;body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tinyurl.com%2Fy4a2veu6" class="social-share-item email" title="Email" target="_blank">Email</a></div><div id="disqus_thread"><noscript><p><a href="http://npr-wkar.disqus.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wkar.org%2Fpost%2Flegalized-sports-betting-horizon-michigan">View the discussion thread.</a></p></noscript></div>        </div>

